1
00:00:22,908 --> 00:00:26,568
The 1000 Eyes of Dr. Mabuse

2
00:00:50,403 --> 00:00:54,066
Screenplay: Fritz Lang and Heinz Oskar Wuttig

3
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,665
Based on an idea by Jan Fethge

4
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,704
Cinematography: Karl Löb

5
00:00:58,905 --> 00:01:02,305
Production Design:
Erich Kettelhut and Johannes Ott

6
00:01:02,506 --> 00:01:06,006
Music: Gerhard Becker

7
00:01:06,107 --> 00:01:08,107
"Schau ich zum Himmelszelt"
composed by Werner Müller

8
00:01:08,507 --> 00:01:10,607
Assistant Director: Walter Wischniewsky

9
00:01:10,708 --> 00:01:12,808
Film Editors: Walter and Waltraut Wischniewsky

10
